After reinstalling, you can update *all* packages stored in *all* `.libPaths()` with the following command

```r
pkgs <- installed.packages( .libPaths() )[,'Package']
install.packages(
    pkgs=pkgs,
    lib=.libPaths()[1],
    type='source'
)
```

You can find all old packages

```r
old.packages(.libPaths())
```
